thread.section_title: Store DJ Reviews | Customer Service Reviews of Store DJ | storedj.com.au
thread.title: Anonymous

author: Anonymous
title: Anonymous
text: A very good range of instruments, cables and audio tools. Prices are reasonable, and are adjusted to current retail trends regularly unlike a few of the other local stores. I like that I can collect my order from the store on the day I ordered of it is in stock. The staff are mostly helpful though a couple do come across as condescending when purchasing items that aren't seen as "pro" audio devices such as the cheaper Korg products.
